“’Ù@fb5501e44d68803e9acd169672787cb64852b6d8302bab62000bbd7fe9798f12ÚTTitle: This week in Nu #86
Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3297] error reporting
, began support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3299] ``into``
 commands
, removed dupes from 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3308] get commands names
, removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3311] help from the commands list in 
``$scope``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3319] sorted 
``$scope``
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3323] ``$scope``
 output
jonathandturner improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3300] range and internal iteration
, more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3301] internal iteration improvements
, split 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3304] OutputStream and ActionStream
, fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3307] regression with auto-conversion
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3320] ``to``
 and 
``from``
 subcommands to new command forms
LhKipp made sure 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3303] the rest arg was available
kubouch improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3305] filepath values
daschl fixed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3309] lib api to allow for custom commands
lucassmg fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3322] ``echo ..``
 from treating 
``..``
 as a range
andrasio wrote up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3326] a guide for creating Nushell commands
